{"NONYL":[{"def":"The hydrocarbon radical, C9H19, derived from nonane and forming many compounds.","pos":""}],"NONYLENE":[{"def":"Any one of a series of metameric, unsaturated hydrocarbons C9H18 of the ethylene series.","pos":""}],"NONYLENIC":[{"def":"Of, pertaining to, related to, or designating, nonylene or its compounds; as, nonylenic acid.","pos":""}],"NONYLIC":[{"def":"Of, pertaining to, or designating, nonyl or its compounds; as, nonylic acid.","pos":""}]}